      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in a state of aesthetic and mechanical preservation that rivals its original showroom delivery. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the meticulously serviced powertrain, reflects a history of fastidious ownership. We invite the most discerning buyers to inspect this unrivaled example of performance and luxury.",
