      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a collector-grade example of the marque\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. The engine features individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced high-pressure VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the 8,000 RPM range. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is superlative, featuring comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. This vehicle exhibits zero fluid migration and a pristine undercarriage, representing a benchmark in mechanical preservation. Finished in its original paint with a flawless interior, it is a purist\u2019s turn-key investment.",
      "price": 48500.0,
